    <h2>The product is still being developed and released, but feedback so far has been positive.</h2>

    <p>From the beginning, the goal was to take what could be a subjective, difficult process, and make it standardized, and easily repeatable. New employees, and eventually even customers themselves, should be able to use the system to make correct product recommendations, with a minimum amount of upfront training.</p>
